            <div class="container grid-3">
                <div class="loc-card">
                    <img src="images/Assets/Cave 01.png" alt="Floating Rock Island" class="loc-img">
                    <h3>Floating Rock Island</h3>
                    <p>Ruthra's secret homeland. The only location with volcanic cliff-formations producing rare
                        Floating
                        Stones (black porous rock) coveted by the Empire for construction.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="loc-card">
                    <img src="images/Assets/Ashram 01.png" alt="Pazhi Tribe Territory" class="loc-img">
                    <h3>Pazhi Tribe Territory</h3>
                    <p>Kshala's home, the Silent Dawn Clan. Underground cave civilization with stone houses carved into
                        walls, lit by natural sun shafts through waterfalls. Ancient source of Yali symbolism.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="loc-card">
                    <img src="images/Assets/Cave 03.png" alt="The Capital" class="loc-img">
                    <h3>The Capital - Mahameru Palace</h3>
                    <p>Tyrannical center of the Empire. Temple complex with enslaved sculptors. The river source behind
                        the
                        palace is key to Ruthra's flood plan.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

