                    <li>Bell Alarm Network - Escape through underwater tunnel triggers Empire surveillance</li>
                    <li>Viruka's Wrath - Rajaguru demands retribution, doubles island tribute</li>
                    <li>Palace Yard Torment - Ruthra witnesses enslaved sculptors being whipped</li>
                    <li>Kitchen Chase - Ruthra saves Kshala stealing food for her kin</li>
                    <li>Elder's Lesson - Pazhi tribe teaching: "Fear takes form; when you face it, it bows"</li>
                    <li>Council Hall - Viruka demands the Island's floating stones</li>
                    <li>The Narabali Prophecy - Sidh learns of royal-blood sacrifice targeting Ruthra</li>
                    <li>The Withdrawal - Ruthra misjudges Sidh's obedience</li>
                    <li>The Truth - Sidh confesses Cheliya's murder, freezing the night</li>
                </ol>

                <div
